---
import { Button } from "./ui/button"
import { MonitorSmartphone, LineChart, Sparkles, Workflow } from "@lucide/astro"
import showcaseImg from "../assets/showcase.png"
---

<section class="showcase-wrapper flex justify-center px-4 py-8 sm:px-8 " id="showcase">
  <div class="showcase-panel relative isolate flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[36px] bg-(--surface-base) text-(--ink-body) shadow-(--shadow-elevated)">
    <div class="showcase-pattern" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="showcase-highlight" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="grid gap-10 p-8 sm:gap-12 sm:p-12 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.05fr)_minmax(0,0.95fr)] lg:items-center lg:gap-14 xl:p-16">
      <div class="showcase-media">
        <div class="showcase-media-frame">
          <img src={showcaseImg.src} alt="Dashboard showcase preview" class="showcase-image" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                    <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center">
            <a
              href="/showcase"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-(--brand-primary) px-24 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-(--brand-primary-dark) shadow-(--shadow-accent) transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-(--brand-primary-hover) focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-(--brand-primary-strong)"
              >実績を見る</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-7">
        <span class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-(--brand-primary-outline) bg-(--brand-primary-soft) px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-(--brand-primary-dark)">
          <span class="inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-(--brand-primary)"></span>
          最新のショーケース
        </span>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-[1.08] tracking-tight text-(--ink-strong) sm:text-4xl lg:text-[2.75rem]">
          結果を生むデザインと実装を、<span class="text-(--brand-primary-strong)">ひとりのWebエンジニアとして</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="showcase-copy space-y-4 text-base text-(--ink-body) sm:text-lg">
          <p>
            要件整理からUI設計、実装、テストまで一貫して担当します。
            使いやすさとコードの美しさを両立し、見る人・使う人の両方に心地よい体験を届けることを目指しています。
          </p>
          <p>
        複数のWebプロジェクトを通じて、読みやすく再利用できるコードとスムーズな開発フローを追求してきました。
          </p>
        </div>

        <ul class="showcase-highlights grid gap-4 pt-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <li class="showcase-highlight-card">
            <span class="icon-badge">
              <MonitorSmartphone class="icon" />
            </span>
            <div>
              <h3>実装しやすいUI設計</h3>
              <p>デザインとコーディングの両面から考え、メンテナンス性の高いUIを構築します。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="showcase-highlight-card">
            <span class="icon-badge">
              <Workflow class="icon" />
            </span>
            <div>
              <h3>軽量で効率的な開発</h3>
              <p>シンプルな構成と自動化を意識し、スピードと品質のバランスを保ちます。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="showcase-highlight-card">
            <span class="icon-badge">
              <Sparkles class="icon" />
            </span>
            <div>
              <h3>統一感のあるビジュアル設計</h3>
              <p>カラーやタイポグラフィ、モーションを整え、プロダクト全体の一貫性を保ちます。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="showcase-highlight-card">
            <span class="icon-badge">
              <LineChart class="icon" />
            </span>
            <div>
              <h3>ユーザー行動を意識した改善</h3>
              <p>実際の利用状況から課題を見つけ、UI/UXを継続的に磨き上げます。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .showcase-panel {
    position: relative;
  }

  .showcase-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: linear-gradient(
        to right,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-outline) 35%, transparent) 1px,
        transparent 1px
      ),
      linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-outline) 35%, transparent) 1px,
        transparent 1px
      );
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    opacity: 0.48;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .showcase-highlight {
    position: absolute;
    width: 360px;
    height: 360px;
    top: -140px;
    left: -120px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-primary) 40%, transparent) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .showcase-panel > .grid,
  .showcase-panel > .grid * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .showcase-highlights {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .showcase-highlight-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    border-radius: 22px;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-outline) 80%, transparent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-base) 96%, transparent);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(12, 18, 32, 0.06);
    transition: transform 0.35s ease, border-color 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
  }

  .showcase-highlight-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-primary) 55%, var(--surface-outline));
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-accent);
  }

  .showcase-highlight-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.3rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-strong);
  }

  .showcase-highlight-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  .icon-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 2.5rem;
    width: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-primary) 22%, var(--surface-base));
    color: var(--brand-primary-dark);
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  .icon {
    width: 1.35rem;
    height: 1.35rem;
  }

  .showcase-media {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .showcase-media-frame {
    /* removed glassmorphism wrapper so the image and SVG sit centered together */
    position: relative;
    width: min(100%, 640px);
    padding: 0;
    border-radius: 0;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    box-shadow: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }



  .showcase-image {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 520px;
    object-fit: contain;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background-color: transparent;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .showcase-wrapper {
      padding-block: 2.5rem;
    }

    .showcase-panel {
      border-radius: 28px;
    }

    .showcase-media-frame {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .showcase-image {
      border-radius: 20px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .showcase-wrapper {
      padding-inline: 1rem;
    }

    .showcase-panel {
      border-radius: 22px;
    }

    .showcase-panel .grid {
      gap: 2.75rem;
    }

    .showcase-media-frame {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .showcase-image {
      border-radius: 18px;
    }
  }
</style>
